text: Schore is a village in the Dutch province of Zeeland. It is located in the municipality of Kapelle, about 8 km southwest of Goes. Schore was a separate municipality until 1941, when it was merged with Kapelle. ==References== ==External links== * Map of the former municipality, around 1868.
